  <brief_title>Nutrition Study of Effect of High Iron Beans on Iron Status</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Iron Biofortified Beans in Improving the Iron Status of Rwandan Adolescent Girls: A Randomized Control Trial</official_title>
