  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether beans bred to have a high iron content are
      effective in improving the iron status of young women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the study is to determine the efficacy of biofortified beans in improving the
      iron status of young women in Rwanda.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
